\ LP format - for model browsing. Use MPS format to capture full model detail.
Minimize
 
Subject To
 R0: X_1 >= 90
 R1: X_1 <= 110
 R2: X_2 >= 32
 R3: X_2 <= 32.2
 R4: X_3 >= 0
 R5: X_3 <= 0
 R6: X_4 >= 10
 R7: X_4 <= 11
 R8: X_5 >= 30
 R9: X_5 <= 30.2
 R10: X_6 >= 0
 R11: X_6 <= 0
 region_dim_0: X_2 <= 28
Bounds
 X_1 free
 X_2 free
 X_3 free
 X_4 free
 X_5 free
 X_6 free
End
